# Generated PNGs are massive (~70MB). The <picture> wrapper serves WebP first (~97% browser support);
# PNG fallback covers only legacy browsers. To keep upload small for Railway, ship WebP only and let
# <picture> degrade gracefully on rare unsupported browsers (image broken instead of falling back to PNG).
public/img/generated/**/*.png
